f\left(x;e_{i}\right) & =\lim_{t\rightarrow0}\frac{f\left(x+te_{i}\right)-f\left(x\right)}{t}=\lim_{t\rightarrow0}\frac{a^{T}\left(x+te_{i}\right)-a^{T}x}{t}=\\
 & =\lim_{t\rightarrow0}\frac{a^{T}x+a^{T}te_{i}-a^{T}x}{t}=\lim_{t\rightarrow0}\frac{a^{T}te_{i}}{t}=\lim_{t\rightarrow0}a^{T}e_{i}=a_{i}
