\end_inset

and for 
\begin_inset Formula $x=-\alpha\frac{a}{\left\Vert a\right\Vert _{2}}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a^{T}x=-a^{T}\alpha\frac{a}{\left\Vert a\right\Vert _{2}}=-\alpha\frac{\left\Vert a\right\Vert _{2}^{2}}{\left\Vert a\right\Vert _{2}}=-\alpha\left\Vert a\right\Vert _{2}
